BillOfExchangeDistributionPosting is an ActionForm
    action is BillOfExchangeDistribution
    Layout
        single column
            VendorGroup
        two column
            PayGroup
                select is PayGroups
            PayGroup.Name
                no label
                display as text
        single column
            PostDate
                label is "PostThroughDate"
        single column
            UpdateOption
                label is "UpdateGlobalLedger"
        header2 of untranslatable:"Report Distribution"
        two column distributed
            column1 of 40%
                BillOfExchangeDistributionReport_RDG
            column2 of 25%
                BillOfExchangeDistributionReport_XPT
